api/                    flask api
├── shop/
│   ├── __init__.py     turns the shop directory into a python package
│   ├── app.py          for creating an instance of the flask app
│   ├── config.py       contains configuration settings for the flask app
│   ├── models.py       for defining classes that will serve as objects in the database
│   └── routes.py       for defining api endpoints, or routes
├── manage.py           access to flask app instance for flask-script and flask-migrate commands
└── run.py              start-up script for running the api app
